1
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:43,750
[Phoenix's Gambit: Love or Crown]

2
00:00:43,910 --> 00:00:46,380
[Episode 6]

3
00:00:46,770 --> 00:00:48,800
My Lady, please have mercy on me.

4
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:51,450
Xiyue, you're in such a refined mood today.

5
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,840
Xiyao, you're at home.

6
00:00:54,870 --> 00:00:57,690
I thought you were at the palace, helping the Empress Dowager.

7
00:00:57,710 --> 00:00:59,340
I just got back

8
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:01,160
and heard that you're playing the guqin,

9
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:02,310
so I came to enjoy it.

10
00:01:02,340 --> 00:01:03,810
My playing skills are rudimentary and unrefined,

11
00:01:03,830 --> 00:01:05,440
unsuitable for a formal performance.

12
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:07,780
Indeed, they're not.

13
00:01:09,500 --> 00:01:10,930
However, I

14
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,970
could perhaps give you some pointers.

15
00:01:14,340 --> 00:01:15,940
You useless fool, with no sense of what's needed!

16
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:17,460
Don't you know you should add some ice?

17
00:01:17,490 --> 00:01:18,640
I know I'm wrong.

18
00:01:18,830 --> 00:01:19,340
But...

19
00:01:19,370 --> 00:01:20,990
but the ice allotted to you in the storehouse

20
00:01:21,010 --> 00:01:22,050
has already been used up.

21
00:01:22,070 --> 00:01:23,680
Then request more from the household.

22
00:01:23,870 --> 00:01:25,330
You can't even handle such a small matter.

23
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:27,020
How can you be my personal maid?

24
00:01:27,070 --> 00:01:28,750
In this scorching summer,

25
00:01:28,780 --> 00:01:30,440
ice is already in short supply

26
00:01:30,470 --> 00:01:31,440
throughout the capital.

27
00:01:32,570 --> 00:01:33,550
Lianxin,

28
00:01:34,380 --> 00:01:35,880
go instruct the storehouse

29
00:01:36,170 --> 00:01:37,440
to spare a couple of pieces

30
00:01:37,470 --> 00:01:39,180
of my share for Second Miss.

31
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:41,270
Also, have the kitchen prepare some iced desserts.

32
00:01:41,300 --> 00:01:42,530
Yes, my Lady.

33
00:01:43,250 --> 00:01:44,880
I've caused you unnecessary expense, Xiyao.

34
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:54,039
Xiyue, the tune you're playing, "Praying to Immortals for Three Lifetimes,"

35
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:55,740
is not the complete version.

36
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:58,580
In fact, the score circulating in the capital

37
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:01,120
has some mistakes and incorrect notes.

38
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:04,330
Xiyao, you know this tune?

39
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,090
I more than merely know it.

40
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:07,750
It won't be until three years later

41
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:09,680
that someone will discover the complete musical score

42
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:11,400
in the ancient archives of the previous dynasty.

43
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,480
I acquired it by chance.

44
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:17,180
I can teach you if you'd like.

45
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,290
I wouldn't dare impose on you, Xiyao.

46
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:23,250
It's just a pastime for me.

47
00:02:23,390 --> 00:02:24,750
Even if I master it,

48
00:02:24,770 --> 00:02:26,380
who would be there to listen?

49
00:02:27,010 --> 00:02:28,470
You could perform it

50
00:02:29,010 --> 00:02:30,770
for the Empress Dowager in the palace.

51
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:36,100
Xiyao, you jest.

52
00:02:36,130 --> 00:02:38,130
I'm not fortunate enough for such an honor.

53
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:40,220
You know Pei Yan has always favored me.

54
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,880
I can ask him

55
00:02:44,900 --> 00:02:46,770
to get you a pass to enter the palace.

56
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,320
When the time comes,

57
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:50,530
I'll bring you to the birthday banquet

58
00:02:50,579 --> 00:02:51,680
so you can perform

59
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:53,290
for the Empress Dowager in public.

60
00:03:01,990 --> 00:03:03,810
Xiyao, what do you truly want?

61
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,740
I've already sent Lianxin off.

62
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:08,850
What do you think?

63
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:22,300
Xiyao, you must have misunderstood something.

64
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:24,700
How could Lianxin be disloyal to you?

65
00:03:24,730 --> 00:03:26,329
After all, she's served you for 10 years.

66
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:29,860
Since you won't help ease my burden,

67
00:03:29,890 --> 00:03:31,760
I'll no longer disturb your practice.

68
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:32,840
Wait, Xiyao.

69
00:03:34,170 --> 00:03:36,840
I did hear from old Steward Gui

70
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:38,960
mention some things about Lianxin.

71
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:42,570
Didn't he retire and return to his hometown?

72
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,180
What did he say?

73
00:03:45,230 --> 00:03:47,260
It's about something from your childhood.

74
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:49,030
Everyone, please don't rush.

75
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:50,930
Each of you will get a bowl of porridge

76
00:03:50,950 --> 00:03:52,020
and a steamed bun.

77
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:53,400
Here you go. Be careful. It's hot.

78
00:03:53,420 --> 00:03:54,430
Steward Gui,

79
00:03:54,450 --> 00:03:55,750
we're out of steamed buns.

80
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:57,280
Please bring two more baskets.

81
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,579
Yes, Lady Xiyao.

82
00:04:00,380 --> 00:04:01,220
Thank you.

83
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:01,950
[Bai's Mansion]

84
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,170
Ma'am,

85
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,070
are they giving out food here?

86
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,440
Yes.

87
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:08,550
Today, the eldest daughter of the Bai family

88
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:09,900
is distributing porridge to refugees.

89
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:10,700
Hurry and get some.

90
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:11,770
The eldest daughter of the Bai family.

91
00:04:16,970 --> 00:04:19,089
[Bai's Mansion]

92
00:04:20,269 --> 00:04:21,130
Thank you.

93
00:04:27,770 --> 00:04:28,860
Okay,

94
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:29,690
brother.

95
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,690
I'll wait for you.

96
