is very similar to that of the little girl back then.

117
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:26,020
What happened to that little mute boy?

118
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,420
He was beaten to death, of course.

119
00:05:28,610 --> 00:05:30,240
After all, he offended you.

120
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,350
Those servants surely

121
00:05:32,370 --> 00:05:34,130
wouldn't have held back.

122
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:37,720
