123
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,580
caused Lianxin's brother's death?

124
00:05:41,450 --> 00:05:42,880
Xiyao, you don't need to blame yourself.

125
00:05:42,909 --> 00:05:44,409
He was just a little beggar, after all.

126
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,570
Even though he was beaten to death,

127
00:05:45,590 --> 00:05:46,360
no one would dare to speak

128
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:48,190
against our family, the household of the Minister of Rites.

129
00:05:49,570 --> 00:05:51,740
