130
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:54,990
just to seek revenge for her brother.

131
00:05:55,130 --> 00:05:57,150
Then, I don't understand.

132
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:59,450
If there is such a deep grudge,

133
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,140
how could Lianxin still enter our household

134
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:02,310
to serve you as a maid?

135
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:05,110
Steward Gui must have mistaken her due to his failing eyesight.

136
00:06:05,530 --> 00:06:07,700
I will investigate the truth of this matter.

137
00:06:08,230 --> 00:06:10,430
I'll have a copy of the music score and send it to your quarters.

138
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:12,590
You should practice more these days.

139
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:14,180
Don't embarrass our family

140
00:06:14,210 --> 00:06:15,750
when you're in the palace performing it.

141
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:17,980
Thank you for your support, sister.

142
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,810
Bai Xiyao,

143
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:25,060
prepare for the deadly showdown

144
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:26,480
between you and your maid.

145
00:06:26,890 --> 00:06:27,790
My Lord,

146
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:29,290
stop staring at it and dwelling on past memories.

147
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:30,260
It's time to take your medicine.

148
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,610
You earned a military post for your achievements in war,

149
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,100
yet you refused to accept it.

150
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:52,070
You insisted on serving me.

151
00:06:52,110 --> 00:06:53,860
Do you just want to watch me make a fool of myself?

152
00:06:54,890 --> 00:06:55,860
I wouldn't dare, my Lord.

153
00:06:56,090 --> 00:06:58,310
I simply wish to serve you for life, my Lord.

154
00:06:58,370 --> 00:06:59,950
No matter how high the position offered, I don't want it.

155
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:02,330
You...

156
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,780
When I saved you back then,

157
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:05,660
I shouldn't have healed your throat.

158
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:07,340
I should have let you remain mute.

159
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,670
You'd be less talkative.

160
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:10,980
My voice was given to me by you, my Lord.

161
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,630
Even this life of mine was given by you.

162
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,260
That's ancient history.

163
00:07:14,650 --> 00:07:15,830
Why bring that up?

164
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:19,490
It's just that your sister

165
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:21,260
still hasn't been found.

166
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,780
Now that we're in the capital,

167
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:26,200
send more people to search for her.

168
00:07:26,230 --> 00:07:27,400
There should be some information soon.

169
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:30,120
Tao Yu will never forget

170
00:07:30,150 --> 00:07:31,480
My Lord's kindness, not even in death.

171
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,990
Get up.

172
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:39,159
How's it going with the matter

173
00:07:39,180 --> 00:07:40,200
I asked you to investigate?

174
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:41,130
My Lord,

175
00:07:41,150 --> 00:07:43,020
10 years ago, only the heiress of the Minister of Rites,

176
00:07:43,050 --> 00:07:44,450
Bai Xiyao, frequented the palace

177
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,409
to attend to the Empress Dowager.

178
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,490
The concubine-born daughter, Bai Xiyue,

179
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,820
never entered the palace.

180
00:07:50,420 --> 00:07:51,600
Since it's her,

181
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:53,620
why was she afraid to admit who she is to me?

182
00:07:54,050 --> 00:07:55,610
And even had her sister pretend to be her.

183
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:58,260
The Minister of Rites is determined to have his daughter marry a prince.

184
00:07:58,730 --> 00:08:01,290
The Empress Dowager also hopes for another queen from the Bai family.

185
00:08:01,620 --> 00:08:03,540
She might be waiting in her boudoir to be married...

186
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,130
so she doesn't want any entanglement with you, my Lord.

187
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,690
That's their thinking.

188
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:14,260
I want to know what Bai Xiyao thinks.

189
00:08:14,850 --> 00:08:16,970
Why don't you go ask her yourself, my Lord?

190
00:08:17,290 --> 00:08:19,290
