191
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:21,630
you could give her the position in the future.

192
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:22,450
Nonsense.

193
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:24,310
I want revenge,

194
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:25,400
