00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,900
to survive!

279
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,230
You old fools.

280
00:10:50,250 --> 00:10:51,690
You already have one foot in the grave.

281
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,920
What's the point of living any longer?

282
00:10:52,950 --> 00:10:53,700
Better to let us younger ones

283
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,780
eat our fill!

284
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,760
Thank you, kind sir.

285
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,260
My Lady,

286
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,670
are you in there?

287
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:00,660
Thank you, kind sir.

288
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,070
May you have many children and blessings.

289
00:11:06,430 --> 00:11:07,900
Do you want us brothers

290
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:08,900
to send you off to your grave?

291
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:09,760
Stop!

292
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,990
Are you alright?

293
00:11:15,930 --> 00:11:17,130
Have you no shame,

294
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,670
stealing food from an old man!

295
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:20,800
Little beauty,

296
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:22,690
there are rules here!

297
00:11:23,790 --> 00:11:24,630
That's right.

298
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:26,990
Miss,

299
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:27,700
you called for me?

300
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:28,630
What are your orders?

301
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:33,100
Bai Xiyao already knows you want revenge against her.

302
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,090
How is that possible?

303
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,350
She's going to the charity hall tomorrow.

304
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:36,870
That's your last chance.

305
00:11:37,130 --> 00:11:38,490
Either she dies

306
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:39,670
or you die.

307
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,600
What...

308
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,120
what should I do?

309
00:11:42,990 --> 00:11:44,730
The area around the charity hall is chaotic.

310
00:11:45,110 --> 00:11:46,240
Find an opportunity

311
00:11:46,260 --> 00:11:47,620
and finish her with one strike.

312
00:11:48,230 --> 00:11:49,030
I...

313
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:50,590
I...

314
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:54,530
When she was distributing porridge back then,

315
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:56,080
she caused your brother's death.

316
00:11:56,210 --> 00:11:57,940
Now, as she distributes porridge again,

317
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,990
it's time for you to avenge your family.

318
00:12:00,020 --> 00:12:02,450
Heaven's justice really comes full circle.

319
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,160
Kill her!

320
00:12:07,490 --> 00:12:09,190
Kill... kill her.

321
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:17,830
Mind your own business!

322
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,810
If I use my celestial power here,

323
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,410
I might faint again afterward.

324
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:23,290
I can't use it unless absolutely necessary.

325
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,430
Shame?

326
00:12:24,770 --> 00:12:26,590
We brothers will show you

327
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:28,870
what real shame is.

328
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:29,800
Miss, don't worry about me.

329
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,700
Run quickly.

330
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,690
I am the eldest daughter of the Minister of Rites!

331
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,800
If you harm me,

332
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:35,000
you will suffer serious consequences!

333
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,930
Boss, it's her.

334
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,060
Let's abduct her.

335
00:12:38,090 --> 00:12:38,830
Let's do it!

336
00:12:41,050 --> 00:12:42,530
Are you alright, Boss?

337
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:43,450
Revenge...

338
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:47,290
I must avenge my brother.

339
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:50,270
This chick has some martial arts skills.

340
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:51,700
Kill this little wench!

341
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:53,430
Brothers, let's go together!

342
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:54,840
Miss!

343
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:55,600
Let go of me!

344
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:57,290
Who are you people?

345
00:13:02,350 --> 00:13:03,280
Get lost.

346
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:04,450
I said, get lost!

347
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,240
Help me...

348
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,320
Run!

349
00:13:06,970 --> 00:13:07,970
My Lady,

350
00:13:07,990 --> 00:13:08,730
run!

351
00:13:09,050 --> 00:13:09,840
Thank you.

352
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:12,220
Thank you, Eldest Miss Bai and this young lady.

353
00:13:14,410 --> 00:13:15,240
Lianxin,

354
00:13:15,490 --> 00:13:16,350
it's alright now.

355
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:17,730
I'll take you home.

356
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,690
No!

357
00:13:19,810 --> 00:13:20,910
I'm going to kill you!

358
00:13:20,930 --> 00:13:22,630
I need to avenge my brother!

359
00:13:22,660 --> 00:13:23,480
Lianxin.

360
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:25,190
I'm also very sorry about what happened to your brother back then.

361
00:13:25,220 --> 00:13:25,690
But back then...

362
00:13:25,710 --> 00:13:26,350
Sorry?

363
00:13:26,430 --> 00:13:28,720
Can an apology bring my brother back to life?

364
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:31,230
I want you to pay with your life!

365
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:33,080
Lianxin.

366
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:35,450
The one you should kill is Bai Xiyue.

367
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:36,550
You've been deceived by her.

368
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:37,610
Nonsense!

369
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,310
Second Miss Xiyue is helping me get revenge.

370
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:43,400
Don't try to drive a wedge between us.

371
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:45,480
Remember when you were helping me serve porridge earlier,

372
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:47,540
and everyone called you "Eldest Miss Bai"?

373
00:13:48,410 --> 00:13:50,310
What exactly are you trying to say?

374
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:51,770
I'll tell you

375
00:13:52,190 --> 00:13:54,580
the part that Bai Xiyue dares not tell you.

376
00:13:54,610 --> 00:13:56,150
Everyone, please don't rush.

377
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:58,530
Each of you will get a bowl of porridge

378
00:13:58,550 --> 00:13:59,720
and a steamed bun.

379
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,330
See?

380
00:14:00,350 --> 00:14:01,620
Mom will distract her in a moment.

381
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:03,010
Then you go and serve porridge in place of your sister.

382
00:14:03,030 --> 00:14:03,830
Be good.

383
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:05,730
I don't want to!

384
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:06,920
They're so dirty!

385
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:08,120
They stink!

386
00:14:08,140 --> 00:14:09,130
Silly girl,

387
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:10,400
you need to earn a good reputation

388
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,020
so that you can marry into a good family in the future.

389
00:14:12,050 --> 00:14:13,470
Even if you don't want to, you must bear with it.

390
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:15,870
Let's go.

391
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,350
Thank you, Eldest Miss.

392
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:18,780
Xiyao,

393
00:14:18,810 --> 00:14:19,860
go and rest for a while.

394
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:20,620
Don't tire yourself out.

395
00:14:20,650 --> 00:14:22,340
Madam, I'm not tired.

396
00:14:22,370 --> 00:14:24,770
I heard that the Duke's son is leaving for the frontier today.

397
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:26,420
Aren't you kind of friends with him?

398
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,350
He's leaving?

399
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:29,900
I'll trouble you to take care of things here, Madam.

400
00:14:29,900 --> 00:14:31,230
I need to go out for a while.

401
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:32,860
Lady Xiyao?

402
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:34,060
Come on, hurry and distribute.

403
00:14:34,090 --> 00:14:36,280
I'll go invite some ladies from noble families to come and see.

404
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:37,500
Be good, okay?

405
00:14:38,070 --> 00:14:39,090
Alright.

406
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,030
Here you go.

407
00:14:40,050 --> 00:14:40,610
Thank you.

408
00:14:40,660 --> 00:14:41,430
Take care.

409
00:14:41,430 --> 00:14:42,830
Okay, okay, okay.

410
00:14:42,830 --> 00:14:43,310
Thank you.

411
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:44,100
No need to rush.

412
00:14:44,180 --> 00:14:44,740
Thank you.

413
00:14:44,770 --> 00:14:45,380
There's enough for everyone.

414
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,240
There's enough for everyone.

415
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:46,730
Come on.

416
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:48,050
Thank you, Eldest Miss.

417
00:14:48,530 --> 00:14:49,300
Why are you pushing?

418
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,200
Stay away from me!

419
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:53,010
Here, be careful.

420
00:14:53,190 --> 00:14:53,900
Okay.

421
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:54,510
Come on.

422
00:14:54,530 --> 00:14:56,140
Thank you, Miss Bai.

423
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:06,400
Everyone can only take one, okay?

424
00:15:09,830 --> 00:15:10,710
What's going on here?

425
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:14,730
You filthy creature!

426
00:15:14,980 --> 00:15:15,990
How dare you splash me!

427
00:15:16,010 --> 00:15:17,290
Catch him!

428
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:19,870
Beat him!

429
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:21,460
-Stinking brat, how dare you splash our young lady?
-Beat this lowlife to a pulp!

430
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:22,260
What are you doing?

431
00:15:22,330 --> 00:15:23,860
Stop hitting him!

432
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:25,060
Brother!

433
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:26,490
Brother!

434
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:27,290
You little mute!

435
00:15:28,610 --> 00:15:29,900
How dare you splash our young lady!

436
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:30,890
Don't grab the buns!

437
00:15:30,890 --> 00:15:31,890
Don't grab the buns! You all!

438
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,940
Brother! Brother!

439
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,450
Let go of me!

440
00:15:37,470 --> 00:15:38,490
Brother!

441
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:39,400
Don't go get yourself killed!

442
00:15:39,430 --> 00:15:40,730
I'll take you somewhere where you can eat your fill!

443
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:41,490
My Lady,

444
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:43,090
this little beggar seems to be dying.

445
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,120
Take him far away.

446
00:15:44,140 --> 00:15:45,710
Don't let him sully the threshold here.

447
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:55,080
Lianxin,

448
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:56,750
think carefully.

449
00:15:57,140 --> 00:15:59,030
When your brother was being beaten back then,

450
00:15:59,050 --> 00:16:00,950
was it my face that you saw?

451
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:02,100
It was you!

452
00:16:02,130 --> 00:16:03,540
There's no way I remembered it wrong!
